        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 21 at 4:27PM EDT by NWS Pittsburgh PA</headline>
        <description>A line of showers and thunderstorms along a cold front may
produce small hail and strong wind gusts up to 40 to 50 MPH
through this evening. Remain weather aware and seek shelter
indoors until any strong thunderstorms pass.
